## рџ“± Android вЂ” Always

- `PROVIDER_GOOGLE` on every `<MapView>`. No exceptions.
- Use `animateToRegion()` for map camera. Never `fitToCoordinates()` or `animateCamera({ zoom })` вЂ” broken on most OEMs.
- `watchPositionAsync` needs both `distanceInterval` AND `timeInterval: 1000` вЂ” Android ignores distance-only.
- `TextInput` always gets `underlineColorAndroid="transparent"`.
- `Pressable` always gets `android_ripple={{ color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)' }}`.
- Font weights: only `'400' '600' '700' '800'` вЂ” Android drops others silently.
- `letterSpacing` needs `includeFontPadding: false` to render right.

