## рџ“Ќ Location

- Always check permissions before requesting. Never request cold.
- Wrap `getCurrentPositionAsync` in an 8s timeout вЂ” it hangs on some Android OEMs.
- GPS quality: `<15m` good В· `15вЂ“30m` warn В· `>30m` bad. Use shared `gpsQuality(acc)` util.

