## рџЋЁ Layout & Safe Area

- Header padding в†’ `Math.max(insets.top, 10)`. Never hardcode.
- Bottom UI padding в†’ `Math.max(insets.bottom, 16)`. Covers gesture bar on Android 10+.
- Any absolute child in a rounded container в†’ parent needs `overflow: 'hidden'`.

