## рџ§© Components

- Small touch targets (<44pt) в†’ always add `hitSlop={12}`.
- Loading + error states в†’ every data-fetching screen gets both. Use shared `<LoadingView />` and `<ErrorView />`.
- Screens with maps/native modules в†’ always wrap in `<ErrorBoundary>`.
- Never pass color/size/style as props if it's already in `constants/`. Import directly.

