## рџ”Ѓ Effects & Async

- Every async effect в†’ cancellation flag (`let cancelled = false`).
- Every subscription/interval в†’ cleaned up in `useEffect` return.
- State needed inside intervals в†’ store in a ref, update ref every render.

---

## рџ“¦ Data

- Every API call в†’ `try/catch/finally`. `finally` always clears loading state.
- Never silently swallow errors. Show `Alert` for user-facing failures.

